[{"title":"FMCW雷达仿真","url":"/2022/10/24/FMCW%E9%9B%B7%E8%BE%BE%E4%BB%BF%E7%9C%9F/","content":"<h1 id=\"FMCW雷达仿真\"><a href=\"#FMCW雷达仿真\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"FMCW雷达仿真\"></a>FMCW雷达仿真</h1><h2 id=\"发射信号模型\"><a href=\"#发射信号模型\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"发射信号模型\"></a>发射信号模型</h2><p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/508764579\">参考教程</a></p>\n<p>线性调频连续波（LFMCW） 雷达发射波形的信号形式为调频连续锯齿波，线性调频的含义即调制信号频率随时间线性变化。从时域上看，是一个频率随时间线性变化的波形；从频域上看， 发射信号的频率与时间成正比， 如下图所示。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/10/24/FMCW%E9%9B%B7%E8%BE%BE%E4%BB%BF%E7%9C%9F/%E5%9B%BE1-1.webp\" alt=\"图1-1 LFMCW锯齿波模型\"></p>\n<center> <div style=\"color:orange; border-bottom: 1px solid #d9d9d9;    display: inline-block;    color: #999;    padding: 2px;\"><font size=\"2px\">LFMCW锯齿波模型</font></div></center>\n\n<p>即信号频率为：</p>\n<script type=\"math/tex; mode=display\">\nf=f_0+ut\\tag{1}</script><p>瞬时相位对时间求导的结果是瞬时角频率（因为相位的变化率即为频率）,所以LFMCW的发射信号模型可用下式表示：</p>\n<script type=\"math/tex; mode=display\">\n\\begin{aligned} S_t(t)=A\\cos \\lbrace2\\pi (f_0 t +ut^2/2) +\\phi _0\\rbrace, t\\epsilon[0,T]\\end{aligned}\\tag{2}</script><h2 id=\"对静止目标测距\"><a href=\"#对静止目标测距\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"对静止目标测距\"></a>对静止目标测距</h2><p>理想情况下，接收信号比发射信号延迟$\\tau=2R/c$，其中目标与雷达距离为$R$，光速为$c$。</p>\n<p>所以理想的回波信号如下式：</p>\n<script type=\"math/tex; mode=display\">\n\\begin{aligned} S_r(t)=KA\\cos \\lbrace2\\pi &\\left[ f_0\\left( t-\\tau \\right) +u\\left( t-\\tau \\right) ^2/2 \\right]\\\\ +\\phi _0\\rbrace, t\\epsilon&[\\tau,T+\\tau]\\end{aligned}\\tag{3}</script><p>二者频率之差（中频）可表示为：</p>\n<script type=\"math/tex; mode=display\">\nf_m=u\\tau=\\frac{u2R}{c}=\\frac{2BR}{cT}\\tag{4}</script><p>对中频信号进行ADC 采样， 然后做 FFT 提取信号的频率信息， 假设 FFT 得到频谱的谱峰值对应的频率为fm ， 则目标的距离信息可以表示如下：</p>\n<script type=\"math/tex; mode=display\">\nR=\\frac{cTf_m}{2B}\\tag{5}</script><h2 id=\"对运动目标测距\"><a href=\"#对运动目标测距\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"对运动目标测距\"></a>对运动目标测距</h2><p>假设，在电磁波的覆盖区域中，某一目标在$t_0$时刻距离发射天线为$R_0$，以径向速度$v$远离天线，以远离天线为正方向。那么接受到目标的回波信号模型公式依旧与单目标一致，如下所示：</p>\n<script type=\"math/tex; mode=display\">\n\\begin{aligned} S_r(t)=KA\\cos \\lbrace2\\pi &\\left[ f_0\\left( t-\\tau \\right) +u\\left( t-\\tau \\right) ^2/2 \\right]\\\\ +\\phi _0\\rbrace, t\\epsilon&[\\frac{2R_0}{c},\\frac{2(R_0+vT)}{c}+T]\\end{aligned}\\tag{6}</script><p>但是，$\\tau$有所改变，如下所示：</p>\n<script type=\"math/tex; mode=display\">\n\\tau=\\frac{2R}{c}=\\frac{2(R_0+vt)}{c}\\tag{7}</script><p>所以通过混频后得到中频信号的相位如下所示：</p>\n<script type=\"math/tex; mode=display\">\n\\begin{aligned} p_t(t)-p_r(t)&=2\\pi f_0\\tau+2\\pi u\\tau t-\\pi u\\tau ^2\\\\&= 2\\pi(\\frac{2f_0v}{c}+\\frac{2uR}{c}-\\frac{4uRv}{c^2})t\\\\&+\\pi(\\frac{4uv}{c}-\\frac{4uv^2}{c^2})t^2+\\frac{4\\pi Rf_0}{c}-\\frac{4\\pi uR^2}{c^2}\\end{aligned}\\tag{8}</script><p>上式中各系数均为常数，t为变量（假设目标匀速运动），可得中频信号依然为线性调频信号。该信号的调频斜率$u_m$，载频$f_m$，初相$\\phi_m$分别如下：</p>\n<script type=\"math/tex; mode=display\">\n\\begin{aligned} u_m=&\\frac{4uv}{c}-\\frac{4uv^2}{c^2}\\\\f_m=&\\frac{2f_0v}{c}+\\frac{2uR}{c}-\\frac{4uRv}{c^2}\\\\\\phi_m=&\\frac{4\\pi Rf_0}{c}-\\frac{4\\pi uR^2}{c^2}\\end{aligned}\\tag{9}</script><p>因为$c=3\\times10^8 m/s$因此可略去分母为$c^2$的项 ，带宽$B_m$为：</p>\n<script type=\"math/tex; mode=display\">\nB_m=u_mT=\\frac{4uv}{c}T=\\frac{4Bv}{c}\\tag{10}</script><p>时宽带宽积$D_m$为（中频信号时宽为发射和回波信号的公共部分）：</p>\n<script type=\"math/tex; mode=display\">\nD_m=B_m\\times(T-\\frac{2R_0}{c})\\tag{11}</script><p>上述公式可以表明，即使目标在几百米每秒的高速运动情况下，中频信号的时宽带宽积仅有原来的$10^{-6}$倍。在宏观低速运动中，$v\\ll c$，因此$B_m\\ll B$，可视为单频信号。综上中频信号可表示为：</p>\n<script type=\"math/tex; mode=display\">\nS(t)=Asin(2\\pi f_0t+\\phi_0)\\tag{12}</script><p>其中，$f_0=\\frac{S2d}{c}$，$\\phi_0=\\frac{4\\pi d}{\\lambda }$</p>\n<p>下面由上述推导的公式来证明，为什么最终会是这个简单的公式呢？将下面的公式去掉光速的平方项，做近似。相位一共就2$\\pi$那么大，速度引起的变化量级为1000；速度对频率的两项引起的变化量级为10000（R项）和100（V项），也就是10000，但频率基数大，一般都要10000以上（1m的距离），所以速度对频率影响的百分比为1，对相位影响的百分比为100，因此相位对速度更敏感，包含的速度信息更多。每一个chirp的fft峰值处的复数的相位即为该chirp中频信号的初相。相邻chirp中频信号的相位差与速度关系如下图。下图中相位差为相邻chirpif信号的相位差也就代表相位变化的快慢，即频率。<img src=\"/2022/10/24/FMCW%E9%9B%B7%E8%BE%BE%E4%BB%BF%E7%9C%9F/image-20221029140629525.png\" alt=\"image-20221029140629525\">如果有128个相邻中频信号，那么相位就会以固定频率w周期性变化。因此对128个chirp的频谱峰值的原复数再做fft，频谱峰值点即为相位变化的频率。由上述分析及上图，可得$v=\\frac{\\lambda }{4\\pi T_c}(2\\pi n/N)$，其中n为N点fft的频谱峰值点。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/10/24/FMCW%E9%9B%B7%E8%BE%BE%E4%BB%BF%E7%9C%9F/image-20221029141039483.png\" alt=\"image-20221029141039483\"></p>\n<p>N点fft的频谱分辨率为$2\\pi/N$。也就与目标速度有对应的正比关系。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/10/24/FMCW%E9%9B%B7%E8%BE%BE%E4%BB%BF%E7%9C%9F/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202022-10-27%20121054.png\" alt></p>\n<p>如果忽略多普勒频率对对中频信号频率的影响（按$f_0$60GHz，目标速度20 $m/s$ ，距离200 $m$ 算，带宽4Ghz，时间40us，多普勒频率也就8000Hz,和中频信号133333Hz不是一个数量级)，则有：</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/10/24/FMCW%E9%9B%B7%E8%BE%BE%E4%BB%BF%E7%9C%9F/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202022-10-27%20121258.png\" alt></p>\n<p>关于上述TI官方给出的中频信号的近似值，就是这么得到的。近似公式忽略 $IF$ 信号的频率与物体速度的依赖关系。在快速$ FMCW $雷达中，其影响通常非常小，且在处理完成多普勒 $FFT$ 后，即可轻松对其进行进一步校正，这就是多普勒相位补偿。</p>\n<h2 id=\"MATLAB解算距离和速度\"><a href=\"#MATLAB解算距离和速度\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"MATLAB解算距离和速度\"></a>MATLAB解算距离和速度</h2><p>假设单个扫描周期 ADC采样点数为 N， 采样频率为Fs， 式中 n 为 FFT 谱峰对应的频点， 根据 T、 Fs、 N 之间的关系(<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/greatwgb/article/details/17913559\">fft物理过程定义参考教程</a>），距离与频率关系的公式可进一步化简为：</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/10/24/FMCW%E9%9B%B7%E8%BE%BE%E4%BB%BF%E7%9C%9F/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202022-10-27%20213750.png\" alt></p>\n<p>($TF_s=N$)式中，$c/2B$为雷达的距离分辨率$ΔR$，</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/10/24/FMCW%E9%9B%B7%E8%BE%BE%E4%BB%BF%E7%9C%9F/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202022-10-27%20215254.png\" alt></p>\n<p>（因为$F_n$所能分辨到频率为$F_s/N=1/T$(<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/greatwgb/article/details/17913559\">fft物理过程定义参考教程</a>）,T为采样时间，$t_c$为扫频时间，二者相等因为一直在采样，但只有有chirp信号的时间段有效）， 可见中频信号的 FFT 谱峰对应的频点，即目标距离门号，乘以距离分辨率就可得到目标的距离。</p>\n<p>上述公式就是在用MATLAB计算目标的距离的时候，我们通常得到的是点的序号（距离门号），而不是直接得到目标的距离，因此需要通过这个公式将距离门号转换成目标真实的距离。</p>\n<p>但是请注意，因为上述的采样点刚好是2的次幂，因此，计算之后系数K刚好为1，假如采样点数不是2的次幂，如200个点，然后256个点的FFT，那么K值就不能等于1了，如下公式所示：</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/10/24/FMCW%E9%9B%B7%E8%BE%BE%E4%BB%BF%E7%9C%9F/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202022-10-27%20220023.png\" alt></p>\n<h1 id=\"matlab仿真程序\"><a href=\"#matlab仿真程序\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"matlab仿真程序\"></a>matlab仿真程序</h1><p>iwr6843aop参数配置：载频60GHz、带宽4GHz</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight matlab\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">%% 雷达系统参数设置</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">%IWR6843aop，载频60Ghz，带宽4Ghz，</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">fc= <span class=\"number\">60e9</span>;             <span class=\"comment\">% 雷达工作频率 载频</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">B = <span class=\"number\">4e9</span>;              <span class=\"comment\">% 带宽4Ghz</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">c = <span class=\"number\">3e8</span>;              <span class=\"comment\">% 光速</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">rangeRes = c / (<span class=\"number\">2</span>*B); <span class=\"comment\">% 雷达的距离分辨率</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>FMCW波形参数：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight matlab\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">%% FMCW波形参数设置</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">Tchirp = <span class=\"number\">40</span>/(<span class=\"number\">64</span>*<span class=\"number\">1e3</span>);       <span class=\"comment\">% 扫频时间 刘师兄毕设，帧周期40ms，每帧64个chirp</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">slope = B / Tchirp;         <span class=\"comment\">% 调频斜率</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">%endle_time=6.3e-8;         % 空闲时间</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">%f_IFmax= (slope*2*maxR)/c ;% 最高中频频率</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">%f_IF=(slope*2*r0)/c ;      % 当前中频频率</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">Nd=<span class=\"number\">128</span>;                         <span class=\"comment\">%每帧chirp数量 </span></span><br><span class=\"line\">Nr=<span class=\"number\">1024</span>;                        <span class=\"comment\">%每个chirp信号中ADC采样点数</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">vres=(c/fc)/(<span class=\"number\">2</span>*Nd*(Tchirp));    <span class=\"comment\">%速度分辨率</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">% Nr=1024*256;                  %和频信号点数设置</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">Fs=Nr/Tchirp;                   <span class=\"comment\">%模拟信号采样频率</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">t1=<span class=\"built_in\">linspace</span>(<span class=\"number\">0</span>,Nd*Tchirp,Nr*Nd*<span class=\"number\">100</span>);<span class=\"comment\">%模拟信号时间</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">t=<span class=\"built_in\">linspace</span>(<span class=\"number\">0</span>,Nd*Tchirp,Nr*Nd);  <span class=\"comment\">%发射信号和接收信号的采样时间，在MATLAB中的模拟信号是通过数字信号无限采样生成的。</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">%m=1/(t(2)-t(1));</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">Tx=<span class=\"built_in\">zeros</span>(<span class=\"number\">1</span>,<span class=\"built_in\">length</span>(t));          <span class=\"comment\">%发射信号初始化</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">Rx=<span class=\"built_in\">zeros</span>(<span class=\"number\">1</span>,<span class=\"built_in\">length</span>(t));          <span class=\"comment\">%接收信号初始化</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">Mix = <span class=\"built_in\">zeros</span>(<span class=\"number\">1</span>,<span class=\"built_in\">length</span>(t));       <span class=\"comment\">%中频信号初始化</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">r_t=<span class=\"built_in\">zeros</span>(<span class=\"number\">1</span>,<span class=\"built_in\">length</span>(t));         <span class=\"comment\">%目标距离</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">td=<span class=\"built_in\">zeros</span>(<span class=\"number\">1</span>,<span class=\"built_in\">length</span>(t));          <span class=\"comment\">%延迟时间</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>TX和RX混频得到IF：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight matlab\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"built_in\">i</span>=<span class=\"number\">0</span>:(Nd<span class=\"number\">-1</span>) <span class=\"comment\">%慢时间</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"built_in\">j</span>=<span class=\"number\">1</span>:Nr <span class=\"comment\">%快时间</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\">    r_t(<span class=\"built_in\">i</span>*Nr+<span class=\"built_in\">j</span>) = r0 + v0*t(<span class=\"built_in\">i</span>*Nr+<span class=\"built_in\">j</span>); <span class=\"comment\">% 距离更新</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    td(<span class=\"built_in\">i</span>*Nr+<span class=\"built_in\">j</span>) = <span class=\"number\">2</span>*r_t(<span class=\"built_in\">i</span>*Nr+<span class=\"built_in\">j</span>)/c;    <span class=\"comment\">% 延迟时间</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    Tx(<span class=\"built_in\">i</span>*Nr+<span class=\"built_in\">j</span>) = <span class=\"built_in\">cos</span>(<span class=\"number\">2</span>*<span class=\"built_in\">pi</span>*(fc*t(<span class=\"built_in\">j</span>) + (slope*t(<span class=\"built_in\">j</span>)^<span class=\"number\">2</span>)/<span class=\"number\">2</span>)); <span class=\"comment\">% 发射信号 实数信号</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    Rx(<span class=\"built_in\">i</span>*Nr+<span class=\"built_in\">j</span>) = <span class=\"built_in\">cos</span>(<span class=\"number\">2</span>*<span class=\"built_in\">pi</span>*(fc*(t(<span class=\"built_in\">j</span>)-td(<span class=\"built_in\">i</span>*Nr+<span class=\"built_in\">j</span>)) + (slope*(t(<span class=\"built_in\">j</span>)-td(<span class=\"built_in\">i</span>*Nr+<span class=\"built_in\">j</span>))^<span class=\"number\">2</span>)/<span class=\"number\">2</span>)); <span class=\"comment\">%接收信号 实数信号</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">%if i&lt;=1024</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">         freq(<span class=\"built_in\">i</span>*Nr+<span class=\"built_in\">j</span>)=fc+slope*t(<span class=\"built_in\">j</span>); <span class=\"comment\">%发射信号</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">         freq_echo(<span class=\"built_in\">i</span>*Nr+<span class=\"built_in\">j</span>)=fc+slope*(t(<span class=\"built_in\">j</span>)-td(<span class=\"built_in\">i</span>*Nr+<span class=\"built_in\">j</span>));<span class=\"comment\">%回波信号频谱延迟</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">%end</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    Mix(<span class=\"built_in\">i</span>*Nr+<span class=\"built_in\">j</span>) = Tx(<span class=\"built_in\">i</span>*Nr+<span class=\"built_in\">j</span>).*Rx(<span class=\"built_in\">i</span>*Nr+<span class=\"built_in\">j</span>);<span class=\"comment\">%差频、差拍、拍频、中频信号混频信号</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">end</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">end</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>距离维和速度维FFT：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight matlab\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">%% 距离维FFT</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">signal=<span class=\"built_in\">reshape</span>(Mix,[Nr,Nd]);</span><br><span class=\"line\">sig_fft = fft(signal,Nr)./Nr;</span><br><span class=\"line\">range_axis = (<span class=\"number\">0</span>:rangeRes:(Nr<span class=\"number\">-1</span>)/<span class=\"number\">2</span>*rangeRes);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">%% 速度维FFT</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">sig_fft2 = fft2(signal,Nr,Nd);</span><br><span class=\"line\">sig_fft2 = fftshift (sig_fft2);</span><br><span class=\"line\">sig_fft2 = sig_fft2(Nr/<span class=\"number\">2</span>+<span class=\"number\">1</span>:Nr,<span class=\"number\">1</span>:Nd)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"仿真结果\"><a href=\"#仿真结果\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"仿真结果\"></a>仿真结果</h1><p><img src=\"/2022/10/24/FMCW%E9%9B%B7%E8%BE%BE%E4%BB%BF%E7%9C%9F/image-20221106144449611.png\" alt=\"image-20221106144449611\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/10/24/FMCW%E9%9B%B7%E8%BE%BE%E4%BB%BF%E7%9C%9F/image-20221106144502356.png\" alt=\"image-20221106144502356\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/10/24/FMCW%E9%9B%B7%E8%BE%BE%E4%BB%BF%E7%9C%9F/image-20221106144513944.png\" alt=\"image-20221106144513944\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/10/24/FMCW%E9%9B%B7%E8%BE%BE%E4%BB%BF%E7%9C%9F/image-20221106144528909.png\" alt=\"image-20221106144528909\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/10/24/FMCW%E9%9B%B7%E8%BE%BE%E4%BB%BF%E7%9C%9F/image-20221106144544465.png\" alt=\"image-20221106144544465\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/10/24/FMCW%E9%9B%B7%E8%BE%BE%E4%BB%BF%E7%9C%9F/image-20221106144555635.png\" alt=\"image-20221106144555635\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/10/24/FMCW%E9%9B%B7%E8%BE%BE%E4%BB%BF%E7%9C%9F/image-20221106144619543.png\" alt=\"image-20221106144619543\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/10/24/FMCW%E9%9B%B7%E8%BE%BE%E4%BB%BF%E7%9C%9F/image-20221106144633393.png\" alt=\"image-20221106144633393\"></p>\n<p>注：实际FMCW雷达发出的相邻chirp信号之间具有延迟时间，目的是在有效探测距离内防止前一个chirp的RX和后一个chirp的TX相混产生其他频率的IF信号（因为目标仍在探测距离内，所以该频率依然在混频后的低通滤波器截止频率前，不会被滤除）。</p>\n","categories":["积累"],"tags":["雷达"]},{"title":"雷达原理-绪论","url":"/2022/10/16/%E9%9B%B7%E8%BE%BE%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86_%E7%BB%AA%E8%AE%BA/","content":"<h1 id=\"雷达原理自学笔记（绪论：P1-P8）\"><a href=\"#雷达原理自学笔记（绪论：P1-P8）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"雷达原理自学笔记（绪论：P1~P8）\"></a>雷达原理自学笔记（绪论：P1~P8）</h1><p>网课链接：<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1zx411h7Tf/?spm_id_from=333.337.search-card.all.click\">西安电子科技大学 雷达原理 全83讲 主讲-魏青 视频教程_哔哩哔哩_bilibili</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"雷达的任务\"><a href=\"#雷达的任务\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"雷达的任务\"></a>雷达的任务</h2><h3 id=\"radar-radio-detection-and-ranging（无线电探测和测距\"><a href=\"#radar-radio-detection-and-ranging（无线电探测和测距\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"radar: radio  detection and ranging（无线电探测和测距)\"></a>radar: radio  detection and ranging（无线电探测和测距)</h3><p>雷达的任务：</p>\n<pre class=\"mermaid\">flowchart LR;\n    id1(雷达任务)---id2(早期);\n    id1(雷达任务)--- id3(现代);\n    id2--- id4(测距);\n    id3---id4;\n    id3---id5(测角);\n    id3---id6(测速);\n    id3---id7(形状);\n\n    classDef default fill:#bbb,stroke:#777, stroke-width:3px;\n    linkStyle 0,1,2,3,4,5,6 stroke: #777, stroke-width:4px,stroke-dasharray:0;</pre>\n\n<p>信息对抗的种类：</p>\n<pre class=\"mermaid\">graph LR;\n    id1(信息对抗)---id2(雷达对抗);\n    id1(信息对抗)--- id3(通信对抗);\n    id1(信息对抗)--- id4(网络对抗);\n    id1(信息对抗)--- id5(光电对抗);\n    classDef default fill:#bbb,stroke:#777, stroke-width:3px;\n    linkStyle 0,1,2,3 stroke: #777, stroke-width:4px;</pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"雷达的基本组成：\"><a href=\"#雷达的基本组成：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"雷达的基本组成：\"></a>雷达的基本组成：</h3><p>天线：发射信号，接受回波</p>\n<p>发射机：产生射频信号</p>\n<p>接收机：接收信号</p>\n<p>信号处理机：提取目标的各种信息</p>\n<pre class=\"mermaid\">flowchart LR;\nid1(\"射频RF(Radio Frequency)\")---id2(\"混频Mixing(相乘)\")---id3(\"中频IF(Intermediate Frequency)\")---id4(视频)\nid5(\"本振LO(Local Oscillator)\")---id2\nclassDef default fill:#bbb,stroke:#777, stroke-width:3px;\nlinkStyle 0,1,2,3 stroke: #777, stroke-width:4px;</pre>\n\n\n\n<p>雷达的工作方式：</p>\n<p>1、连续波：连续波是激光器以连续方式而不是脉冲方式输出的波，这种波形可以是非调制的也可以是调制的。</p>\n<p>2、脉冲：脉冲波是在时间上不连续的，激光地以间断的方式进行辐射的波。</p>\n<p>脉冲雷达的参数定义：</p>\n<p>1、脉冲宽度$\\tau$:单个脉冲持续时间。</p>\n<p>2、脉冲重复周期$T_r$:相邻脉冲的时间间隔。</p>\n<p>雷达测距原理：测量发射信号$S_t(t)$和接收信号$S_r(t)$之间的延迟时间$t_r$</p>\n<script type=\"math/tex; mode=display\">\nt_r=\\frac{2R}{c}</script>","categories":["积累"],"tags":["雷达"]},{"title":"雷达原理-雷达基本原理","url":"/2023/01/16/%E9%9B%B7%E8%BE%BE%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86_%E9%9B%B7%E8%BE%BE%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86/","content":"<h1 id=\"雷达原理自学笔记（雷达基本原理：P9-P10）\"><a href=\"#雷达原理自学笔记（雷达基本原理：P9-P10）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"雷达原理自学笔记（雷达基本原理：P9~P10）\"></a>雷达原理自学笔记（雷达基本原理：P9~P10）</h1><p>网课链接：<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1zx411h7Tf/?spm_id_from=333.337.search-card.all.click\">西安电子科技大学 雷达原理 全83讲 主讲-魏青 视频教程_哔哩哔哩_bilibili</a></p>\n","categories":["积累"],"tags":["雷达"]}]